Package UserCode.Manager

Interface Summary
IEntityListManager IEntityListManager defines the behaviour of a class that will add and remove IEntites from the simulation based on the parameters provided.
IEntityManager IEntityManager defines the beheviour of a manager of IEntities within the aquarium simulation.
IManager IManager defines the behaviour for the top level manager required to run an aquarium simulation.
ISoundManager ISoundManager defines the behaviour a concrete implementation should place an audio file for an Env world
ISubEntityMngr ISubEntityMngr defines the behaviour of classes that require the main List on IEntity's that are present in the aquarium
IWorldManager IWorldManager defines the behaviour of a concrete class that should be able to add and remove instances of IToken's from the world
 

Class Summary
CollisionManager CollisionManager defines the behaviour of a class that detects for 'collisions' between IEntities.
CollisionManagerTest The test class CollisionManagerTest for testing the CollisionManager production class.
EntityListManager EntityListManager defines the concrete implementation of IEntityListManager and ISubEntityMngr.
EntityListManagerTest The test class EntityListManagerTest for testing the production class EntityListManager.
EntityManager EntityManager: The manager controls all the entities within the aquarium by calling each ISubEntityMngr checkEntities method on every frame
EntityManagerTest The test class EntityManagerTest for testing EntityManager.
FeedManager FeedManager defines the behaviour of a class that detects if any of the pets with the IComponent feed have come into contact with a pet with the IComponent FoodFall
FeedManagerTest The test class FeedManagerTest for testing the FeedManager production class.
Manager Manager: This class controls which top level managers are required to run the aquarium simulation.
ManagerTest The test class ManagerTest for testing the production class Manager.
MouseManager MouseManager defines the behaviour of a class that watches an IObserver mouse click handler implementation.
MouseManagerTest The test class MouseManagerTest for testing the production class MouseManager.
PreyLvlManager PreyLvlManager defines the behaviour of a class that checks the amount of pets with the IComponent Prey.
PreyLvlManagerTest The test class PreyLvlManagerTest for testing the PreyLvlManager production class.
SoundManager SoundManager class used to play audio within the simulation
SoundManagerTest The test class SoundManagerTest, for testing SoundManager.
WorldBoundsManager WorldBoundsManger defines the behaviour of a class that detects if any of the IEntity's have left the aquarium on the x & y axis.
WorldBoundsManagerTest The test class WorldBoundsManagerTest for testing the WorldBoundsManager production class.
WorldManager WorldManager defines the class which manages the world by added and removing objects from the simulation.
WorldManagerTest The test class WorldManagerTest for testing the production class WorldManager.
